    "Our algorithm auditing study focuses on two topics that we let our participants converse with the GPT-3 chatbot: climate change and Black Lives Matter (BLM).",
    "The first topic represents a classic controversial science issue across the globe.",
    "Research has shown how public perceptions toward it vary across populations.",
